<font size = "6" > <h3> <li>List Tag </li></h3> </font>
<p> <font size = "6"> List tag is commonly known as bullaten point , containts 2 types of list order and unorder list <br> 
<b> Order list </b> </br> which contains bullten like (1 ,2 ,3) (I ,II ,III) (i , ii , iii) (a, b ,c) <br> 
<ol>
<li> One </li>
<li> Two </li>
<li> Three </li>
<li> Four </li>
<li> Five </li>
</ol>
<ol type = "I">
<li> One </li>
<li> Two </li>
<li> Three </li>
<li> Four </li>
<li> Five </li>
</ol>
<b> Unorder list </b> <br> list containts bulleten like (circle , triangle , square) <br>
<ul>
<li> One </li>
<li> Two </li>
<li> Three </li>
<li> Four </li>
<li> Five </li>
</ul>
<ul type = "square">
<li> One </li>
<li> Two </li>
<li> Three </li>
<li> Four </li>
<li> Five </li>
</ul>
</p>
</font>
</ul>



